homePage._1:
IMS is a unique closed-loop electronic manufacturing intelligent management solution.
Through the optimization process in the electronics manufacturing industry, with intelligent manufacturing as the core concept, it provides a series of unique management methods and management tools,
Improve production efficiency, improve product quality, shorten production cycles, reduce manufacturing costs, comprehensively prevent errors and fools, and achieve comprehensive scientific traceability management.
